{
  "name": "WF4 — Onboarding Nuevo Gym (SaaS)",
  "meta": { "description": "Se dispara cuando un gym owner completa el checkout de su plan SaaS. Crea el registro en la tabla gyms. Crea el perfil del owner. Envía email + WhatsApp de bienvenida. Maqueta lista — solo agrega credenciales." },
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "sticky-onb",
      "name": "📋 INSTRUCCIONES",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [0, -200],
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## WF4 — Onboarding Nuevo Gym\n\n**Credenciales requeridas:**\n1. `Supabase Grind` — URL + Service Role Key\n2. `WHATSAPP_TOKEN` + `WHATSAPP_PHONE_ID` — Env vars\n3. `SMTP Grind` — Credencial SMTP\n4. `SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY` — Env var\n\n**Quién llama este webhook:**\n- El WF1 (SaaS path), después de activar el plan\n- O directamente desde el route `/api/onboarding` del frontend\n\n**URL del Webhook:**\nhttps://aop00.app.n8n.cloud/webhook/grind-onboarding\n\n**Payload esperado:**\n```json\n{ \"ownerName\": \"str\", \"ownerEmail\": \"str\", \"ownerPhone\": \"str\", \"gymName\": \"str\", \"planId\": \"str\", \"userId\": \"uuid\" }```",
        "height": 320,
        "width": 500
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "onb1",
      "name": "🆕 Webhook: Nuevo Gym",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 1.1,
      "position": [560, 300],
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "path": "grind-onboarding",
        "responseMode": "responseNode",
        "options": {}
      },
      "webhookId": "grind-onboarding"
    },
    {
      "id": "onb2",
      "name": "🏋️ CREATE gym en Supabase",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.supabase",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [780, 300],
      "credentials": { "supabaseApi": { "name": "Supabase Grind ← AGREGAR CREDENCIAL" } },
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "create",
        "tableId": "gyms",
        "dataToSend": "defineBelow",
        "fieldsUi": {
          "fieldValues": [
            { "fieldId": "owner_id",    "value": "={{ $json.userId }}" },
            { "fieldId": "name",        "value": "={{ $json.gymName }}" },
            { "fieldId": "slug",        "value": "={{ $json.gymName.toLowerCase().replace(/[^a-z0-9]/g, '-') }}" },
            { "fieldId": "plan_id",     "value": "={{ $json.planId || 'starter' }}" },
            { "fieldId": "plan_status", "value": "trial" },
            { "fieldId": "plan_expires_at", "value": "={{ new Date(Date.now() + 14*24*60*60*1000).toISOString() }}" },
            { "fieldId": "currency",    "value": "MXN" },
            { "fieldId": "timezone",    "value": "America/Mexico_City" },
            { "fieldId": "country_code","value": "MX" },
            { "fieldId": "features",    "value": "={\"fitcoins\":true,\"waitlist\":true,\"fiscal\":false,\"qrAccess\":true}" }
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "onb3",
      "name": "👤 UPDATE profile: asignar gym_id",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.supabase",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [1000, 300],
      "credentials": { "supabaseApi": { "name": "Supabase Grind ← AGREGAR CREDENCIAL" } },
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "update",
        "tableId": "profiles",
        "filterType": "string",
        "filterString": "id=eq.{{ $('onb1').item.json.userId }}",
        "dataToSend": "defineBelow",
        "fieldsUi": {
          "fieldValues": [
            { "fieldId": "gym_id", "value": "={{ $json.id }}" },
            { "fieldId": "role",   "value": "admin" }
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "onb4",
      "name": "📧 Email: Bienvenida + Credenciales",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.emailSend",
      "typeVersion": 2.1,
      "position": [1220, 200],
      "credentials": { "smtp": { "name": "SMTP Grind ← AGREGAR CREDENCIAL" } },
      "parameters": {
        "sendTo": "={{ $('onb1').item.json.ownerEmail }}",
        "subject": "🎉 ¡Bienvenido a Grind Project, {{ $('onb1').item.json.ownerName.split(' ')[0] }}!",
        "emailType": "html",
        "message": "=<h1>¡Tu gym ya está activo!</h1><p>Hola <strong>{{ $('onb1').item.json.ownerName.split(' ')[0] }}</strong>,</p><p>Tu gimnasio <strong>{{ $('onb1').item.json.gymName }}</strong> ha sido registrado en Grind Project.</p><h2>Próximos pasos:</h2><ol><li>Accede a tu panel: <a href='{{ $env['APP_URL'] }}/admin'>{{ $env['APP_URL'] }}/admin</a></li><li>Personaliza tu marca (logo, colores)</li><li>Crea tus primeras clases</li><li>Invita a tus socios</li><li>Conecta tu cuenta de Mercado Pago en Configuración → Pagos</li></ol><p>Plan: <strong>{{ $('onb1').item.json.planId }}</strong></p><hr/><p>Equipo Grind Project</p>"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "onb5",
      "name": "📱 WhatsApp: Bienvenida",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [1220, 420],
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "=https://graph.facebook.com/v18.0/{{ $env['WHATSAPP_PHONE_ID'] }}/messages",
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headerParameters": {
          "parameters": [{ "name": "Authorization", "value": "=Bearer {{ $env['WHATSAPP_TOKEN'] }}" }]
        },
        "sendBody": true,
        "contentType": "json",
        "bodyParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            { "name": "messaging_product", "value": "whatsapp" },
            { "name": "to", "value": "=52{{ $('onb1').item.json.ownerPhone?.replace(/[^0-9]/g, '') }}" },
            { "name": "type", "value": "text" },
            { "name": "text", "value": "={\"body\": \"🎉 ¡Hola {{ $('onb1').item.json.ownerName.split(' ')[0] }}! Tu gym *{{ $('onb1').item.json.gymName }}* ya está activo en Grind Project.\\n\\n👉 Entra a tu panel: {{ $env['APP_URL'] }}/admin\\n\\n¿Tienes dudas? Responde este mensaje.\" }" }
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "onb6",
      "name": "✅ Respond: gym creado",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.respondToWebhook",
      "typeVersion": 1.1,
      "position": [1440, 300],
      "parameters": {
        "respondWith": "json",
        "responseBody": "={ \"success\": true, \"gymId\": \"{{ $('onb2').item.json.id }}\" }",
        "options": { "responseCode": 201 }
      }
    }
  ],
  "connections": {
    "🆕 Webhook: Nuevo Gym":               { "main": [[{ "node": "🏋️ CREATE gym en Supabase",       "type": "main", "index": 0 }]] },
    "🏋️ CREATE gym en Supabase":           { "main": [[{ "node": "👤 UPDATE profile: asignar gym_id", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]] },
    "👤 UPDATE profile: asignar gym_id":   { "main": [[{ "node": "📧 Email: Bienvenida + Credenciales", "type": "main", "index": 0 }], [{ "node": "📱 WhatsApp: Bienvenida", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]] },
    "📧 Email: Bienvenida + Credenciales": { "main": [[{ "node": "✅ Respond: gym creado",           "type": "main", "index": 0 }]] },
    "📱 WhatsApp: Bienvenida":             { "main": [[{ "node": "✅ Respond: gym creado",           "type": "main", "index": 0 }]] }
  },
  "settings": { "executionOrder": "v1" },
  "tags": [{ "name": "grind-project" }, { "name": "onboarding" }]
}
